        "QMB automatically qualifies your parent for Medicare Part D Extra Help prescription drug assistance",
        "Income limits include a $20 disregard that's already factored into the stated amounts",
        "Providers cannot legally bill QMB beneficiaries for Medicare deductibles or coinsurance — if this happens, contact Kentucky Medicaid Services"
