          "question": "Can I apply for SCSEP and other programs like SNAP at the same time?",
          "answer": "Yes, SCSEP participants can apply for and receive other benefits like SNAP, Medicaid, and LIHEAP. The part-time income from SCSEP will be counted when determining eligibility for other programs, but it shouldn't disqualify your parent from most assistance programs due to the low income level."
